Package de.zbmed.snoke.uima.analysis

Custom implementations of analysis engines and their components for the UIMA framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConceptMapper
    The ConceptMapper is an analysis engine that tags named entities based on synonyms for concept names from a dictionary file.
    DictTerm_Agrovoc
    Custom DictTerm_Agrovoc to uniquely assign tags from the Agrovoc dictionary.
    DictTerm_DrugBank
    Custom DictTerm_DrugBank to uniquely assign tags from the DrugBank dictionary.
    DictTerm_EPILONT
    Custom DictTerm_EPILONT to uniquely assign tags from the EPILONT dictionary.
    DictTerm_EpSO
    Custom DictTerm_EpSO to uniquely assign tags from the EpSO dictionary.
    DictTerm_ESSO
    Custom DictTerm_ESSO to uniquely assign tags from the ESSO dictionary.
    DictTerm_MeSH
    Custom DictTerm_MeSH to uniquely assign tags from the MeSH dictionary.
    SentenceAnnotation
    Custom SentenceAnnotation to tag sentences.
    SentenceAnnotation_Type
    Custom SentenceAnnotation_Type for having a unique tag for sentences.
    TokenAnnotation
    Custom TokenAnnotation for having a unique tag for tokens.
    TokenAnnotation_Type
    Custom TokenAnnotation_Type for having a unique type of tag for tokens.
    TokenizerZBMED
    Simple class to tokenize a string (similar to java.util.StringTokenizer), except that this tokenizer returns TokenAnnotation objects, which, in addition to the token text string, also contain the start and end offsets of the token in the original string.
    TokenizerZBMED.Maker  
    WhitespaceTokenizer
    Custom analysis engine WhitespaceTokenizer creating tokens separated by whitespaces in text.
    ZBMEDConceptMapper
    Custom analysis engine ZBMEDConceptMapper with the basic functionality of the ConceptMapper that assigns tags based on synonyms from the dictionary file.
    ZBMEDSnowballAnnotator
    Custom analysis engine ZBMEDSnowballAnnotator that stems tokens based on the Snowball stemming algorithm.
